metadata.name: I AM WONDA
metadata.description:
WONDA by Sun-Min + David

Created for toy projects in 2002, Wonda is a photographer with a 28mm lens and a magic roll of film. This magic roll of 36 photos, in both monochrome and color, will always tell the truth. 

This collection is comprised of 3 works of NFT art about Wonda, and his 36 photos.
